These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, pall-mall, tiparillo, bluemaster, vegafina, dunhill, montecristo
The people have 7 different hobbies: baking, collecting, fishing, gardening, rock-climbing, singing, skydiving
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, cricket, golf, skateboarding, surfing, swimming
The people use 7 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski, quad-bike, ship, subway, train, van
 1. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 3. the person driving the subway is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 4. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 5. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 6. the pall-mall-smoker is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 7. the person driving the van is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 8. the person driving the ship is between the person driving the van and the person who's hobby is singing##2
 9. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
10. the tiparillo-smoker is in the middle##1
11. the person who's sport is baseball is the vegafina-smoker##1
12. the vegafina-smoker is the person driving the bike##1
13. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
14. the person who's hobby is singing is the person driving the quad-bike##1
15. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
16. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
17. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
18. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
19. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Cigar      | pall-mall  | dunhill        | vegafina | tiparillo      | bluemaster     | chaman      | montecristo     |
| Hobby   | collecting | gardening         | skydiving   | baking | singing    | rock-climbing | fishing |
| Sport         | cricket | skateboarding | baseball | basketball | swimming  | surfing  | golf    |
| Transport     | subway  | train         | bike     | jet-ski    | quad-bike | ship     | van     |

