 9. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
10. the fan of metal is between the fan of indie and the person who's birthday is in february##2
11. the fan of disco is the person who's birthday is in october##1
12. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
13. the fan of pop is between the person who's birthday is in february and the fan of reggae##2
14. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
15. the person who likes coral is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
16. the person who likes orange is on the far left##1
17. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
18. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
19. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
20. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person who likes coral and the person who's birthday is in april##2

